			<h6 class="credit">Moises Saman for The New York Times</h6>
				            <p class="caption">Lori Berenson, 41, the American woman who was imprisoned in Peru for more than 14 years for her association with the Tupac Amaru Revolutionary Movement in during the 1990’s.                            </p>
</div>
				

		</div>
